text: Han Jeong-uh (; born 26 December 1998) is a South Korean footballer who plays as midfielder for Suwon FC in the K League 2. ==Career== On 26 January 2019, FC Kairat announced the signing of Han on a two-year contract. On 6 January 2020, Kairat announced via Instagram that Han had been released by the club.
